ActNorthwest Territories Act
SubjectOrder Prohibiting the Issuance of Interests in Public Lands in the Northwest Territories (Central & Eastern Portions of the South Slave Region)
PrecisORDER PROHIBITING THE ISSUANCE OF INTERESTS IN PUBLIC LANDS IN THE NORTHWEST TERRITORIES (CENTRAL AND EASTERN PORTIONS OF THE SOUTH SLAVE REGION) in order to protect all of the lands that were selected as part of Athabasca Denesuline out-of-court settlement agreement negotiations with the Government of Canada, from the establishment of new third party interests.
